{"tid":874134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港珠澳大橋開通】央行發行面值10元銀質紀念幣","createTime":"2018-10-24T03:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T11:00:04.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7caab388d65e764f6290f592e58544ff235fbe0e","tid":874134,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:16:35.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平在珠海宣布「港珠澳大橋正式開通！」<br />\n<br />\n大橋正式通車，中國人民銀行在同日起發行面值10元（人民幣．下同）的港珠澳大橋通車銀質紀念幣。<br />\n<br />\n該紀念幣正面圖案是中華人民共和國國徽，並有國名及2018年年號，背面圖案則為港珠澳大橋主體工程青州航道橋主塔、江海直達船航道橋及人工島建築，代表香港、珠海、澳門三地的紫荊花、三角梅及蓮花。並有「港珠澳大橋通車紀念」中、英文字樣及面額。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，該銀質紀念幣為精制幣，圓形，含純銀30克，直徑40毫米，成色99.9%，最大發行量2萬枚。由深圳國寶造幣有限公司鑄造及中國金幣總公司總經銷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/250377/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E9%96%8B%E9%80%9A-%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%89%E5%B0%87%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%9A%E8%BB%8A-%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%80%BC10%E5%85%83%E9%8A%80%E8%B3%AA%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E5%B9%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BA%258B%2F250377%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%2580%259A-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A1%258C%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%2580%25BC10%25E5%2585%2583%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E5%25B9%25A3&d=gdSRabkEe1ynn%2FDb2mZ3o9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=4b2f09c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/250377/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E9%96%8B%E9%80%9A-%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%89%E5%B0%87%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%9A%E8%BB%8A-%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%80%BC10%E5%85%83%E9%8A%80%E8%B3%AA%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E5%B9%A3</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.airmb.com/html/7/2018/1022/64184.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.airmb.com%2Fhtml%2F7%2F2018%2F1022%2F64184.html&d=gdSRabkEe1ynn%2FDb2mZ3o9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=dcea0fc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.airmb.com/html/7/2018/1022/64184.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中國央行至今只發行過兩項有關建築工程的紀念幣<br />\n<br />\n一個係青藏鐵路全線通車紀念金幣與銀幣<br />\n另外就係長江三峽工程紀念金幣與銀幣<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋是第三個因建築工程而發行的紀念幣"},{"pid":"08cf21db1b4ab99a18eb05e92ebe1028b1110bad","tid":874134,"uid":128271,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:22:42.000Z","msg":"仲有心機印銀紙 <br />\n遲啲都眨晒值做廢紙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1a02366d67fd6eb4f93a0770a7730fd74010e2","tid":874134,"uid":213877,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"08cf21db1b4ab99a18eb05e92ebe1028b1110bad","tid":874134,"uid":128271,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:22:42.000Z","msg":"仲有心機印銀紙 <br />\n遲啲都眨晒值做廢紙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:24:25.000Z","msg":"你係咪白痴嫁？呢D時候唔印幾時印？"},{"pid":"e3e41fffcd5e204dba46d1fd39059e3784065fe5","tid":874134,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:38:26.000Z","msg":"似乎中共對此工程很重視。"},{"pid":"ee1db9212446cfe1e16d31de88bea4a3daf8180e","tid":874134,"uid":133522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:40:40.000Z","msg":"核突到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26dc647a95608558578c9ae9750d11d10ff0000","tid":874134,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:41:32.000Z","msg":"能被磁石吸起的銀幣？"},{"pid":"ed0c17dde177bd73fa265b68282e7c5a3c2791e8","tid":874134,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08cf21db1b4ab99a18eb05e92ebe1028b1110bad","tid":874134,"uid":128271,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03